data.title: ESRI ArcGIS Online
data.meta_description: ArcGIS Online provides ArcGIS users with a set of foundation services that are deeply integrated with ArcGIS. As an ArcGIS user, you have immediate access to map services, task services, software developer kits (SDKs), and other content via the Web. ArcGIS Online services are available as standard, no-cost services for internal and noncommercial external use. ArcGIS Online Sharing is a central Web-based repository through which ArcGIS users can easily search and share GIS, maps, layers, and tools.
